text: Kurmanayevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Bolshesukhoyazovsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 428 as of 2010. There are 14 streets. == Geography == It is located 30 km from Mishkino, 1 km from Bolshesukhoyazovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Kurmanayevo, Mishkinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
